snippet.title: intrusion 2 gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Intrusion 2 is an action platformer with lots of physics.
Available for Windows on Steam! http://store.steampowered.com/app/214970/
Also DRM-free on my site: http://www.intrusion2.com/ 

Programming, art, design by Abramenko Aleksey.
Featuring music by George Dziov's Android - http://georgedziov.com/
